# ESP32 / PlatformIO Conventions

- Framework: PlatformIO with Arduino
- Shared libraries: `iot/common/lib/` (mqtt_client, wifi_manager, sensor_base)
- Each sensor node: `iot/sensor-node/` structure (copy as template)
- Config: `include/config.h` per node

## Project Structure per Node

```
iot/<node-name>/
├── src/main.cpp
├── include/config.h
├── platformio.ini
└── lib/              (symlink or copy from iot/common/lib/)
```

## Naming

- Functions: `camelCase`
- Constants/defines: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`
- Classes: `PascalCase`

## MQTT Topics

Pattern: `happy/<node-type>/<node-id>/<measurement>`

Example: `happy/sensor/1/temperature`
